where yÀÜ ùëó is the class probability for the class index ùëó, and C is a set of considered classes (ùëê ‚àà C).

As shown in Eq. (2), the loss function used in cross entropy-based training methods are used as

a function of the final output yÀÜ, and thus are not designed for SC frameworks. While Eshratifar

